    {
      "id": "33016b10-7e55-46e9-8c31-e863d11452d6",
      "recording_id": "feb43be0-6b73-40c6-84b8-9c448eb49938",
      "end_time": 63.44,
      "start_time": 60.25,
      "recording_attendee_id": "7526f347-d638-4d32-b2d6-8da6f095e981",
      "order_number": 15,
      "text": "So, um I appreciate you jumping on."
    },
    {
      "id": "33016b10-7e55-46e9-8c31-e863d11452d6",
      "recording_id": "feb43be0-6b73-40c6-84b8-9c448eb49938",
      "end_time": 66.11,
      "start_time": 63.45,
      "recording_attendee_id": "7526f347-d638-4d32-b2d6-8da6f095e981",
      "order_number": 16,
      "text": "I know Julia is working on the contract with you guys."
    },
    {
      "id": "33016b10-7e55-46e9-8c31-e863d11452d6",
      "recording_id": "feb43be0-6b73-40c6-84b8-9c448eb49938",
      "end_time": 66.65,
      "start_time": 66.12,
      "recording_attendee_id": "7526f347-d638-4d32-b2d6-8da6f095e981",
      "order_number": 17,
      "text": "Right."
    },
    {
      "id": "33016b10-7e55-46e9-8c31-e863d11452d6",
      "recording_id": "feb43be0-6b73-40c6-84b8-9c448eb49938",
      "end_time": 66.92,
      "start_time": 66.73,
      "recording_attendee_id": "7526f347-d638-4d32-b2d6-8da6f095e981",
      "order_number": 18,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "id": "33016b10-7e55-46e9-8c31-e863d11452d6",
      "recording_id": "feb43be0-6b73-40c6-84b8-9c448eb49938",
      "end_time": 71.85,
      "start_time": 67.22,
      "recording_attendee_id": "7526f347-d638-4d32-b2d6-8da6f095e981",
      "order_number": 19,
      "text": "And I know the intention of course, is to roll out Aton quickly."
    },
    {
      "id": "33016b10-7e55-46e9-8c31-e863d11452d6",
      "recording_id": "feb43be0-6b73-40c6-84b8-9c448eb49938",
      "end_time": 73.44,
      "start_time": 72.61,
      "recording_attendee_id": "7526f347-d638-4d32-b2d6-8da6f095e981",
      "order_number": 20,
      "text": "I don't know."
    },
    {
      "id": "33016b10-7e55-46e9-8c31-e863d11452d6",
      "recording_id": "feb43be0-6b73-40c6-84b8-9c448eb49938",
      "end_time": 73.91,
      "start_time": 73.45,
      "recording_attendee_id": "7526f347-d638-4d32-b2d6-8da6f095e981",
      "order_number": 21,
      "text": "And I,"
    },
    {
      "id": "33016b10-7e55-46e9-8c31-e863d11452d6",
      "recording_id": "feb43be0-6b73-40c6-84b8-9c448eb49938",
      "end_time": 79.21,
      "start_time": 75.91,
      "recording_attendee_id": "7526f347-d638-4d32-b2d6-8da6f095e981",
      "order_number": 22,
      "text": "what we discussed, I'd like largely confidential, but"
    },
    {
      "id": "33016b10-7e55-46e9-8c31-e863d11452d6",
      "recording_id": "feb43be0-6b73-40c6-84b8-9c448eb49938",
      "end_time": 83.75,
      "start_time": 80.73,
      "recording_attendee_id": "7526f347-d638-4d32-b2d6-8da6f095e981",
      "order_number": 23,
      "text": "some, I, I think you'll understand the pieces that are more important than others."
    },
    {
      "id": "33016b10-7e55-46e9-8c31-e863d11452d6",
      "recording_id": "feb43be0-6b73-40c6-84b8-9c448eb49938",
      "end_time": 87.51,
      "start_time": 83.76,
      "recording_attendee_id": "7526f347-d638-4d32-b2d6-8da6f095e981",
      "order_number": 24,
      "text": "But did, were you aware that Aton was in a contract with Radix?"
    },
    {
      "id": "33016b10-7e55-46e9-8c31-e863d11452d6",
      "recording_id": "feb43be0-6b73-40c6-84b8-9c448eb49938",
      "end_time": 91.79,
      "start_time": 91.62,
      "recording_attendee_id": "7526f347-d638-4d32-b2d6-8da6f095e981",
      "order_number": 25,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "id": "33016b10-7e55-46e9-8c31-e863d11452d6",
      "recording_id": "feb43be0-6b73-40c6-84b8-9c448eb49938",
      "end_time": 92.33,
      "start_time": 91.8,
      "recording_attendee_id": "7526f347-d638-4d32-b2d6-8da6f095e981",
      "order_number": 26,
      "text": "They,"
    },
    {
      "id": "33016b10-7e55-46e9-8c31-e863d11452d6",
      "recording_id": "feb43be0-6b73-40c6-84b8-9c448eb49938",
      "end_time": 96.45,
      "start_time": 92.34,
      "recording_attendee_id": "03cc0415-5406-451b-bc44-1ebd7970a4c6",
      "order_number": 27,
      "text": "so they had told us that they were moving on from RADI, they are moving on from RADI."
    },
    {
      "id": "33016b10-7e55-46e9-8c31-e863d11452d6",
      "recording_id": "feb43be0-6b73-40c6-84b8-9c448eb49938",
      "end_time": 97.74,
      "start_time": 96.59,
      "recording_attendee_id": "03cc0415-5406-451b-bc44-1ebd7970a4c6",
      "order_number": 28,
      "text": "That is a fact"
    },
    {
      "id": "33016b10-7e55-46e9-8c31-e863d11452d6",
      "recording_id": "feb43be0-6b73-40c6-84b8-9c448eb49938",
      "end_time": 106.81,
      "start_time": 97.86,
      "recording_attendee_id": "7526f347-d638-4d32-b2d6-8da6f095e981",
      "order_number": 29,
      "text": "and they indicated to us that you were going to wave apartment IQ up until their contract with RADI terminated."
    },
    {
      "id": "33016b10-7e55-46e9-8c31-e863d11452d6",
      "recording_id": "feb43be0-6b73-40c6-84b8-9c448eb49938",
      "end_time": 114.17,
      "start_time": 106.82,
      "recording_attendee_id": "7526f347-d638-4d32-b2d6-8da6f095e981",
      "order_number": 30,
      "text": "In which case the, the payments would start at that point, which is September October is that accurate"
    },
    {
      "id": "33016b10-7e55-46e9-8c31-e863d11452d6",
      "recording_id": "feb43be0-6b73-40c6-84b8-9c448eb49938",
      "end_time": 117.48,
      "start_time": 115.58,
      "recording_attendee_id": "7526f347-d638-4d32-b2d6-8da6f095e981",
      "order_number": 31,
      "text": "so that I, I was not aware of that"
    },
    {
      "id": "33016b10-7e55-46e9-8c31-e863d11452d6",
      "recording_id": "feb43be0-6b73-40c6-84b8-9c448eb49938",
      "end_time": 117.96,
      "start_time": 117.49,
      "recording_attendee_id": "03cc0415-5406-451b-bc44-1ebd7970a4c6",
      "order_number": 32,
      "text": "part."
    },
    {
      "id": "33016b10-7e55-46e9-8c31-e863d11452d6",
      "recording_id": "feb43be0-6b73-40c6-84b8-9c448eb49938",
      "end_time": 121.41,
      "start_time": 119.27,
      "recording_attendee_id": "03cc0415-5406-451b-bc44-1ebd7970a4c6",
      "order_number": 33,
      "text": "Um Are you having the"
    },
    {
      "id": "33016b10-7e55-46e9-8c31-e863d11452d6",
      "recording_id": "feb43be0-6b73-40c6-84b8-9c448eb49938",
      "end_time": 122.72,
      "start_time": 121.42,
      "recording_attendee_id": "7526f347-d638-4d32-b2d6-8da6f095e981",
      "order_number": 34,
      "text": "conversations with them?"
    },
    {
      "id": "33016b10-7e55-46e9-8c31-e863d11452d6",
      "recording_id": "feb43be0-6b73-40c6-84b8-9c448eb49938",
      "end_time": 125.45,
      "start_time": 123.78,
      "recording_attendee_id": "7526f347-d638-4d32-b2d6-8da6f095e981",
      "order_number": 35,
      "text": "So we had had the"
    },
    {
      "id": "33016b10-7e55-46e9-8c31-e863d11452d6",
      "recording_id": "feb43be0-6b73-40c6-84b8-9c448eb49938",
      "end_time": 129.68,
      "start_time": 125.46,
      "recording_attendee_id": "03cc0415-5406-451b-bc44-1ebd7970a4c6",
      "order_number": 36,
      "text": "conversations with them for their properties with Will Bridge."
    },
    {
      "id": "33016b10-7e55-46e9-8c31-e863d11452d6",
      "recording_id": "feb43be0-6b73-40c6-84b8-9c448eb49938",
      "end_time": 137.43,
      "start_time": 130.61,
      "recording_attendee_id": "03cc0415-5406-451b-bc44-1ebd7970a4c6",
      "order_number": 37,
      "text": "Um, and then I hadn't directly spoke with, um, I know my associate Justin, who's"
    },
    {
      "id": "33016b10-7e55-46e9-8c31-e863d11452d6",
      "recording_id": "feb43be0-6b73-40c6-84b8-9c448eb49938",
      "end_time": 142.41,
      "start_time": 138.54,
      "recording_attendee_id": "03cc0415-5406-451b-bc44-1ebd7970a4c6",
      "order_number": 38,
      "text": "the wil Bridge end is because he has the Will Bridge account."
    },
    {
      "id": "33016b10-7e55-46e9-8c31-e863d11452d6",
      "recording_id": "feb43be0-6b73-40c6-84b8-9c448eb49938",
      "end_time": 147.48,
      "start_time": 142.42,
      "recording_attendee_id": "03cc0415-5406-451b-bc44-1ebd7970a4c6",
      "order_number": 39,
      "text": "But, um, as far as talking with, I haven't directly talked with anybody yet."
    },
    {
      "id": "33016b10-7e55-46e9-8c31-e863d11452d6",
      "recording_id": "feb43be0-6b73-40c6-84b8-9c448eb49938",
      "end_time": 149.83,
      "start_time": 148.9,
      "recording_attendee_id": "03cc0415-5406-451b-bc44-1ebd7970a4c6",
      "order_number": 40,
      "text": "I don't know what agreements"
    },
    {
      "id": "33016b10-7e55-46e9-8c31-e863d11452d6",
      "recording_id": "feb43be0-6b73-40c6-84b8-9c448eb49938",
      "end_time": 150.29,
      "start_time": 149.84,
      "recording_attendee_id": "7526f347-d638-4d32-b2d6-8da6f095e981",
      "order_number": 41,
      "text": "have been made."
    },
    {
      "id": "33016b10-7e55-46e9-8c31-e863d11452d6",
      "recording_id": "feb43be0-6b73-40c6-84b8-9c448eb49938",
      "end_time": 157.04,
      "start_time": 150.3,
      "recording_attendee_id": "7526f347-d638-4d32-b2d6-8da6f095e981",
      "order_number": 42,
      "text": "I just want to make sure that when we're reviewing this contract, that whatever is done on the Aton spectrum is done with whatever agreement was made."
    },
    {
      "id": "33016b10-7e55-46e9-8c31-e863d11452d6",
      "recording_id": "feb43be0-6b73-40c6-84b8-9c448eb49938",
      "end_time": 159.91,
      "start_time": 157.24,
      "recording_attendee_id": "7526f347-d638-4d32-b2d6-8da6f095e981",
      "order_number": 43,
      "text": "Abington has obviously asked that we proceed forth."
    },
    {
      "id": "33016b10-7e55-46e9-8c31-e863d11452d6",
      "recording_id": "feb43be0-6b73-40c6-84b8-9c448eb49938",
      "end_time": 176.41,
      "start_time": 159.92,
      "recording_attendee_id": "7526f347-d638-4d32-b2d6-8da6f095e981",
      "order_number": 44,
      "text": "I totally agree with their position to make the change and some of the highlights for them of course, is confirming or for me, I need to confirm that again that they're, we're gonna roll out the product but that they're not going to be invoiced until their contract with radix expires."
    },
    {
      "id": "33016b10-7e55-46e9-8c31-e863d11452d6",
      "recording_id": "feb43be0-6b73-40c6-84b8-9c448eb49938",
      "end_time": 182.92,
      "start_time": 176.57,
      "recording_attendee_id": "7526f347-d638-4d32-b2d6-8da6f095e981",
      "order_number": 45,
      "text": "And then secondly, I know Julia and you are Julia with Pegasus, you've been working on the contract and she sent to me where you're at."
    },
    {
      "id": "33016b10-7e55-46e9-8c31-e863d11452d6",
      "recording_id": "feb43be0-6b73-40c6-84b8-9c448eb49938",
      "end_time": 185.49,
      "start_time": 182.93,
      "recording_attendee_id": "7526f347-d638-4d32-b2d6-8da6f095e981",
      "order_number": 46,
      "text": "Are we largely done with that contract?"
    },
    {
      "id": "33016b10-7e55-46e9-8c31-e863d11452d6",
      "recording_id": "feb43be0-6b73-40c6-84b8-9c448eb49938",
      "end_time": 188.37,
      "start_time": 186.57,
      "recording_attendee_id": "7526f347-d638-4d32-b2d6-8da6f095e981",
      "order_number": 47,
      "text": "I mean, we got everything back"
    },
    {
      "id": "33016b10-7e55-46e9-8c31-e863d11452d6",
