      "recording_attendee_id": "7526f347-d638-4d32-b2d6-8da6f095e981",
      "order_number": 70,
      "text": "So I I am going to follow up with Julia and our council today to see if we can get this across the finish line if you can internally talk to your team and check about what the invoicing situation is gonna be for Abington property specifically."
