      "start_time": 248.56,
      "recording_attendee_id": "7526f347-d638-4d32-b2d6-8da6f095e981",
      "order_number": 71,
      "text": "And then the last thing is, is Aton is very keen on making sure that we can roll this out in 2 to 3 weeks and have it launched and ready to roll."
