      "recording_attendee_id": "7526f347-d638-4d32-b2d6-8da6f095e981",
      "order_number": 85,
      "text": "I just, I wanted to confirm what you knew and I wanted to confirm, I'm operating as the liaison between Pegasus and between Abington to make sure I'm getting all the utmost accurate information and you were my resource."
    },
