      "recording_attendee_id": "03cc0415-5406-451b-bc44-1ebd7970a4c6",
      "order_number": 89,
      "text": "and that definitely, I mean, we would work with you as far as you know, getting Abington situated and then obviously we wanna have a great partnership going forward too."
